title: All Utilities Paid!!!!!!
map_address: 10222 Walton Walker Blvd near Technology blvd
posting_body: ['Welcome to Budget Suites where you can make one of our apartments your home for a week or beyond!', 'Budget Suites invites you to relax and unwind in your own personal apartment whether you are relocating to a new city, a business traveler, vacationer, or just making a new start here in Dallas.', 'Our apartments are spacious, comfortable and equally affordable for any budget.', 'Our properties are designed to serve you with many amenities including;', 'all utilities paid', 'full sized kitchens and appliances', 'pool and spa', 'laundry facilities', 'with courtesy patrol', 'cable television which includes premium channels; HBO, ESPN and much more.', 'Budget Suites has the conveniences of a hotel, with all the comforts of home.', 'We welcome you to your new home.', 'At every Budget Suites you will find the same valuable services at a price you can value just as much.']
